column2: select s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, s.subclass, s.ra, s.dec, spp.snr FROM SpecObjAll as s, SpecPhotoAll as ph, sppParams as spp where s.SPECOBJID = spp.SPECOBJID and spp.SPECOBJID = ph.specObjID and (s.ra, s.dec) in (select s.ra, s.dec from SpecObjAll where s.class = # group by s.ra, s.dec having count (*) > #) order by s.ra
